Maintainer: Adam T. Kocsis <adam.t.kocsis@gmail.com>
Description: The purpose of the 'chronosphere' project is to increase reproducibility and establish version tracking of results from (paleo)environmental/ecological research. The inherent database maps data files and import code to programming classes and allows access to these items via files deposited in public repositories.  
